### 所有醫師
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors

###

### 單一醫師
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D001

###

### 所有病患
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patients

###

### 所有掛號
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments

###

### 掛號統計
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/count

###

### 新增醫師
POST http://localhost:8080/api/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctorId": "D999",
  "name": "測試醫師",
  "department": "測試科",
  "specialty": "API 測試"
}

###

### 修改醫師
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "更新醫師",
  "department": "內科",
  "specialty": "高血壓"
}

###

### 刪除醫師
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D999